  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its siting, scale and detailed design, would result in an obtrusive, overbearing and incompatible form of development which would fail to respect the character and appearance of the subject properties and the immediate area of which it forms part.&amp;nbsp; As such the proposed development is contrary to policy D4 &#x27;Delivering good design&#x27; of the London Plan (2021) and Policy LP1 &#x27;Design Quality and Local Character&#x27;&amp;nbsp; of the Hackney Local Plan and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its scale, massing and siting, would comprise an overbearing and overly dominant development, to the detriment of the living conditions of residential occupiers by way of a loss of light, outlook and increased sense of enclosure, contrary to Hackney Local Plan (LP33) policies LP1, LP2, LP17, London Plan (2021) Policy D6 and Hackneys &#x27;Residential Extensions and Alterations&#x27; SPD (2009).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
